I had a bit more when I was at Market Drayton, I can't remember how much. But I had a bit more. But I mean I didn't spend - much in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2051906 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7097265\charrsid14362210 Can you remember what you would spend it on?
