Very very good. I didn't know him much until I came back to the Hanley shop, to the main - head shop. I didn't know him much when I w
as at Market Draytin, he had a manager - and I knew him but I didn't know the boss - until I came back to the Hanley shop. And I was there from - oh - seventeen to twenty-two. A marvellous boss.
