No, we used to go to the pictures sometime. Perhaps once a week and then perhaps you get it twice a week. 'Course you cou
ld go to the pictures those days very cheap with a ticket about tuppence. You see, and we - we used to do that but - I was never - I never used to go out a lot walking about - a lot. 'Cos most of our time was - there was any - pleasure it was down at the 
church hall see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2051906 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7097265\charrsid14362210 Doing what particularly?
