belonged to church as well you know, and then she got married, she - met a priest - from our church, and she got married and went to Africa. And I didn't bother with anybody after that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2051906 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7097265\charrsid14362210 Did you not have any boyfriends?
